# Environment Variables — UnVibe

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values.

## PostHog Analytics

Get your API key at https://posthog.com → Settings → Project → Keys

```
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_your_api_key_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://app.posthog.com
```

## Google Gemini AI (Optional — for AI-powered games)

Get your API key at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials

```
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
```

## GitHub Token (Optional — for private repo access)

Generate at https://github.com/settings/tokens

```
GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_your_token_here
```
